oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Slide Collection - Printer's Alley
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Historic Printer's Alley was named for the many printing businesses once located there. However, it is better known for its nighttime entertainment at clubs such as the Rainbow Room, the Carousel, the Voo Doo Lounge and The Embers. 35 mm
